name: World Banner - Gray
description:
Our gray shirts are 90% cotton and 10% polyester, so they may be subject to some shrinkage given that we do not pre-wash our shirts. Just follow the wash instructions on the shirt, and that should do the job! 

*All sizes correspond to mens.

Shipping usually takes 2-3 business days.

----------------------------------------------------------------------------------------

More than 800 million individuals from sub-Saharan Africa, Southeast Asia, and Latin America all need our help in the effort against unsafe drinking water. Join us, and you can be the change you want to the see in the world!

Photographs done by Lens Eye Media
www.lenseyemedia.com
